social_posts.post_text: Going on 4 years I’ve been the biggest fan of @officialkearaalyse and the @thevasifamily still need to come down to Houston and record a song y’all reply to your emails…..
My number 1 city for music in 2023 has been my birth city Houston, even though I’ve barely been in Texas this year according to @spotify #spotifywrapped

2018 was the last time honestly I was heavy in music. Since then a lot has changed. I had just got out of Jail after leaving Texas a month after @nipseyhussle died and was in Savannah Georgia fucked up lost everything, cars, house, relationship no direction no hope and slick lost myself along the way. Looking back I wasn't ready for success no matter how much I wanted it at 26 I got way too much way too fast. The Maturity didn't catch up with the skill sets. After 6 more years of ups and downs I have honestly never been more focused and happy along with confident in the future. Everyone wants to skip past the speed bumps and go right to the finish line but it should be known "The Game is going to Test you it's ups and downs" Once you drown out all the bullshit and focus on the end goal, the other bullshit distractions don't matter on your road to where you meant to be. I'm happy for all the lessons, adversity and people along the journey even if you not around anymore. Just know the focus and determination will drive you to your destination when all else fails. Above all else be proud of where you started and embrace the journey to where you are going. It's the ultimate satisfactory feeling along this Marathon of life......
Every time I post this reel @universalmusicgroup Flags and blacklists it but the last 6 month I have really been feeling like the "Until The End Of Time" video in every aspect.....

Fun fact @where_mikejones actually inspired the name for my "Unknown Ep, 1 & 2" from back in the day with that "Who is Mike Jones" campaign that also explains the [?] Looking backs it's actually crazy that I have a song with one of the Houston Artists I looked up to heavy growing up and kickstarted the whole industry being on the Texas Music wave.....

Everyone looks to rush into dating to fill voids and insecurities they have in themselves. Sometimes it's better to work on becoming the best version of yourself first before incorporating another human into your bs. I can't lie at times it can get lonely because Humans are naturally social creatures but you need the right people with the right headspace to be in your circle in order to grown/bloosm/bloom into the flower you were meant to be. We were born in this world along and sometimes even I fight depression but we are going to continue to press forward no matter what. What's meant to be/ meant for you will come to you at the time it is supposed to, until then don't skip the process. Learn to be the best YOU that you can be....

@daysulan said it best. This is my last somewhat Political post because I didn't sign up to be a politician. I am a Business man first and foremost and this has nothing to do with Democrat/Republican-Gay-Straight none of that stupid shit. The number 1 problem with NARCISSISTIC people (besides the Entitlement Mentality) is the fact that they simply can't take ACCOUNTABILITY. Something as simple as Something is changing or something is wrong let me actively do something to find a solution to the problem let me cry and complain about it like a 2 year old until I possibly get my way. It's literally like dealing with Adult Children. That is the problem with the Government giving people excess Stimulus checks, Eviction Moratoriums, Excess Food Stamps. Mofo's get a Mentality of I am OWED something just because I exist. As a business owner if something is wrong it is your job to actively find out what the problem is, and actively come up with a solution to the problem. Pointing the finger at someone else makes me lose all respect for you as an adult because it proves that you need someone else to take care of all your problems. ACCOUNTABILITY ACCOUNTABILITY ACCOUNTABILITY..... Let me do something to at least try and fix my problem instead of misplacing my anger and frustration somewhere else.......
I play chess..... I'll do a nigga the same way T.I. did Lil Flip. Kill your Career with that "What You Know" video than sign the whole City of Houston to his label
